Cloud API[1].  Given that you have the URI to a particular resource (which
was discovered by being retrieved from some previous representation, and the
representations include URIs to &quot;interesting&quot; related resources -- no URI
templates here), the documentation describes &quot;what kind of requests can I
submit to this URI&quot;?

Craig McClanahan

